{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"63377e8789fb953a","type":"text","text":"**ACTIVITIES**","x":-1380,"y":140,"width":930,"height":60,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"d75819189e3f2523","type":"text","text":"**Select candidate participants via village meeting**. Program staff organization village meetings to conduct Participatory Wealth Ranking, and villagers below some income threshold are selected for site visit.","x":-1380,"y":510,"width":250,"height":280},
		{"id":"c00f6fc8931dc92b","type":"text","text":"**Final participant selection.** Program staff visit candidate participants home to verify information, and then select final participants for program based on existing assets and need. ","x":-1380,"y":843,"width":250,"height":260},
		{"id":"701a6c55372d000b","type":"text","text":"**Transfer assets to participants.** Program staff procure and transfer assets to participants.","x":-1060,"y":793,"width":250,"height":132},
		{"id":"6bb76180619a9725","type":"text","text":"**Identify target villages**. Research staff find poor regions using national survey data, and narrow down to subset of poorest villages to target in consultation with program staff or area experts.","x":-1380,"y":240,"width":250,"height":230},
		{"id":"712d75292d734f43","type":"text","text":"**Identify assets for participants**. Program staff confer with participants to determine which asset they should receive based on list of best options","x":-1060,"y":510,"width":250,"height":215},
		{"id":"91daefecb0f204b6","type":"text","text":"**Asset training.** Program staff or hired experts teach participants how to successfully generate income using asset.","x":-700,"y":260,"width":250,"height":180},
		{"id":"f680860885c4b368","type":"text","text":"**Regular home visits.** Program staff visit participants homes to provide accountability, encouragement, health education, and financial capability education.","x":-700,"y":815,"width":250,"height":220},
		{"id":"49d6b8d6b5d11685","type":"text","text":"**Savings assistance.** Program staff help provide savings account, conduct field visits to allow saving, or help establish savings groups. ","x":-700,"y":1075,"width":250,"height":200},
		{"id":"c179607e34f48a6e","type":"text","text":"**Health training.** Program staff or hired experts provide health, nutrition and hygiene training, and help provide access to health services through enrollment in other programs.","x":-700,"y":1295,"width":250,"height":240},
		{"id":"bb605f82b24a8776","type":"text","text":"**Outputs**","x":-350,"y":140,"width":250,"height":60,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"34a93bcdf399ceb2","type":"text","text":"**Participant accountability and motivation.**","x":-350,"y":855,"width":250,"height":140},
		{"id":"a7197e0a47343aaa","type":"text","text":"**Savings.** Participants increase their savings.","x":-350,"y":1125,"width":250,"height":100},
		{"id":"5b7601664387af4b","type":"text","text":"**Improved health capacity.** Participants gain knowledge and resources that allows them to maintain better health.","x":-350,"y":1335,"width":250,"height":160},
		{"id":"407769778a98380a","type":"text","text":"**Outcomes**","x":0,"y":140,"width":660,"height":60,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"fa36d6a993aae6fc","type":"text","text":"**Identify best assets to transfer.** Research staff or local market experts identify best asset transfer options.","x":-1060,"y":275,"width":250,"height":160},
		{"id":"696e1a90d86fbf26","type":"text","text":"**Increased consumption.** Participants have more money to spends on goods and services they need/want. ","x":420,"y":275,"width":240,"height":180},
		{"id":"2b83a48e2920f8d6","type":"text","text":"**Improved somatic health.** Participants have better health if they adopt health knowledge and resources.","x":0,"y":1340,"width":250,"height":150},
		{"id":"b340d3a3a12cedd1","type":"text","text":"**Income/wealth generating capital.** Participants receive an asset that allow them to generate income or increase wealth.","x":-350,"y":260,"width":250,"height":180},
		{"id":"d58ea6d0bb6dde6b","type":"text","text":"**Improved skills.** Participants gain useful skills for producetivley using the asset.","x":-350,"y":470,"width":250,"height":175},
		{"id":"723f33931ecb5bb4","type":"text","text":"**Stabilizing income**. Participants receive $24 to $72 monthly stipend during the early stages of the program.","x":-350,"y":662,"width":250,"height":160},
		{"id":"3d86712337d321ec","type":"text","text":"**Provide initial consumption support.** This is carried out by program staff. However, the paper does not detail how consumption support is delivered, either manually or electronically.","x":-700,"y":510,"width":250,"height":258},
		{"id":"5234f895bbd9ba8d","type":"text","text":"**Increased asset wealth.** Partcipants have assets that can be sold in case of shock.","x":0,"y":245,"width":250,"height":120},
		{"id":"e1e875e4f91e8bb8","type":"text","text":"**Increased savings.** Participants have more savings in case of shocks.","x":0,"y":1110,"width":250,"height":130},
		{"id":"be9e2eaaf12420b1","type":"text","text":"**Income from asset.** Participants use their asset to generate an income.","x":0,"y":480,"width":250,"height":138},
		{"id":"5f19c1c4d1ec363c","type":"text","text":"**Increased human capital.** Participants have better skills, bodily and psychological capacity for making an income.","x":0,"y":679,"width":250,"height":246},
		{"id":"fea522afa43cdffd","type":"text","text":"**Improved wellbeing.** Participants can afford more things they need/want, have better somatic health, and reduced psychological burden.","x":788,"y":556,"width":250,"height":338},
		{"id":"6c0db517529f0991","type":"text","text":"**Impact**","x":721,"y":140,"width":385,"height":60,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"49324c291ff32a6f","type":"text","text":"**Increased resilience to shocks**. Participants have more resource in the face of shocks.","x":420,"y":558,"width":240,"height":160},
		{"id":"65f83fbec93a707f","type":"text","text":"**Reduced psychological burden from preciarity.** Withi increased wealth and savings, participants can be less psychologically worried  from lack of resources of necessities or lack of resilience to shocks.","x":420,"y":842,"width":240,"height":307}
	],
